00:19:00.080 --> 00:19:03.710
actually gotten better with the combination of PD-1 blockade with CTLA-4 blockade,

333
00:19:04.160 --> 00:19:06.780
and those response rates and cure rates are even higher.

334
00:19:06.800 --> 00:19:09.680
But what about other scenarios? And one scenario that

