00:19:15.420 --> 00:19:18.600
And it really pivots off the idea of minimal residual disease.

337
00:19:18.660 --> 00:19:20.140
And what is minimal residual disease?

338
00:19:20.200 --> 00:19:23.900
Well, the folks in heme malignancies understand this concept very well.

339
00:19:23.940 --> 00:19:27.740
This is a concept that is really coming to vogue in solid

340
00:19:27.800 --> 00:19:31.420
