449
00:25:23.912 --> 00:25:26.512
2020, and we continued enrollment through 2023.

450
00:25:27.632 --> 00:25:30.812
And so we closed the placebo arm, and then we were off to the races.

451
00:25:32.412 --> 00:25:34.692
So the second thing is, these were the early days.

