00:25:51.592 --> 00:25:55.072
And what we found that is actually we could use any assay to define who was

459
00:25:55.112 --> 00:25:56.132
positive and who was negative.

460
00:25:57.852 --> 00:26:00.972
And so Yelena and her team screened 174 patients

